snippet.title: Another Super Mario Bros. Wii - World 1 (100%, Multiplayer)
snippet.description:
This is our 100% Walkthrough of World 1 from Another Super Mario Bros. Wii for the Nintendo Wii. We collect all Star Coins and secret exits.

Another Super Mario Bros. Wii is mod for New Super Mario Bros. Wii created by Skawo and released in December 2010 which includes a full set of new levels with the same themes as the original game.

Timestamps for all the levels:
01:21 - World 1-1
04:11 - World 1-2
09:12 - World 1-3
12:50 - World 1-3 Secret Exit
15:06 - World 1-Tower
18:33 - World 1-4
23:35 - World 1-5
26:08 - World 1-6
30:16 - World 1-Castle

Thanks for watching and subscribe if you want to see more videos!

Mario played by Maurits.
Blue Toad played by Rik.
Yellow Toad played by Myrte.
